		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">The Art of Role Playing Part 1</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=322552" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top"><div style= "padding:4;float: right"> <script language=JavaScript src=http://www.obsidian-tech.com/absolutebm/abmx.aspx?z=26></script></div><p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    <Blockquote>
Guest writer Joseph "Neverly" Christopher sends along a special guest editorial, The Simple Art of Online Role Playing: A Practical Guide. Along with the extended title, he gives some insight into getting started in online RPG's.<P>
 
<a href="http://www.evilavatar.com/EA/Editorials/Games/M27504/">http://www.evilavatar.com/EA/Editorials/Games/M27504/</a><P>
  
-Philip
</blockquote>
