	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				There is roleplaying in EQ.<BR>
<BR>
As a player in the game, you have the option to roleplay or not.<BR>
<BR>
Roleplaying isn't for everyone.<BR>
<BR>
Personally, I enjoy roleplaying. Simple flourishes like the emoticons and a &quot;accent&quot; in typing dialog in say,group,shouts,etc, IMHO, add to the &quot;virtual&quot; reality of the game.<BR>
<BR>
I don't consider it &quot;annoying&quot;. I don't discriminate against classes or races because they are &quot;evil&quot;. <BR>
<BR>
You can roleplay in the game. It's a personal choice. It can be done without bothering others that get their enjoyment from wealth and power.<BR>
<BR>
This is a roleplaying game. If you want to be powerful and kill things, there are other games that would accomodate this philosophy more readily that EQ. <BR>
<BR>
Thank you for your time.<BR>
<BR>
IG Thank ya lads and lasses fer lettin' tha ol' bear tell ya how ah feel abouts tha matta.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
